{
  "version": "1",
  "slug": "komodo",
  "kind": "compose",
  "metadata": {
    "name": "Komodo",
    "description": "Build and deployment automation tool for managing software across multiple servers. Komodo provides\nunlimited server connections, flexible API access, and comprehensive management of Docker deployments,\nstacks, and builds. Features include real-time container monitoring, batch operations, and integration\nwith Docker, Docker Compose, and build systems. Supports both MongoDB and FerretDB as database backends.\n## Important Notes\n* Requires MongoDB or FerretDB for data storage (database not included in this template)\n* Requires Periphery agent on managed servers for remote operations\n* Web interface and API accessible through configured ports\n## References\n* **Project:** https://github.com/moghtech/komodo\n* **Documentation:** https://github.com/moghtech/komodo/tree/main/docsite/docs\n* **Docker Hub:** https://hub.docker.com/r/moghtech/komodo\n",
    "tags": [
      "traefik",
      "swarm",
      "deployment",
      "automation"
    ],
    "author": "Christian Lempa",
    "template_version": "latest",
    "icon": {
      "provider": "mdi",
      "id": "rocket-launch-outline"
    },
    "draft": true,
    "date": "2025-11-13",
    "next_steps": "### 1. Prerequisites\n* Deploy MongoDB or FerretDB database\n* Configure database connection in environment variables\n* Install Periphery agent on servers you want to manage\n### 2. Deploy the Service\n{% if swarm_enabled -%}\nDeploy to Docker Swarm:\n```bash\ndocker stack deploy -c compose.yaml komodo\n```\n{% else -%}\nStart Komodo using Docker Compose:\n```bash\ndocker compose up -d\n```\n{% endif -%}\n### 3. Access the Web Interface\n{% if traefik_enabled -%}\n* Navigate to: **https://{{ traefik_host }}.{{ traefik_domain }}**\n{% else -%}\n* Navigate to: **http://localhost:{{ ports_http }}**\n{% endif -%}\n* Complete initial setup and create admin user\n### 4. Install Periphery Agent\nOn each server you want to manage:\n```bash\ncurl -sSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/moghtech/komodo/main/scripts/setup-periphery.py | python3\n```\n### 5. Configure Servers\n* Add servers to Komodo through the web interface\n* Configure API keys for programmatic access\n* Start managing deployments, stacks, and builds\n"
  },
  "entrypoint": {
    "path": "compose.yaml",
    "type": "file"
  },
  "variables": [
    {
      "key": "general",
      "title": "General",
      "variables": [
        {
          "name": "service_name",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Service Name",
          "required": false,
          "default": "komodo"
        },
        {
          "name": "container_name",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Container Name",
          "required": false,
          "default": "komodo"
        },
        {
          "name": "container_hostname",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Container Hostname",
          "required": false,
          "default": "komodo"
        },
        {
          "name": "restart_policy",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Restart Policy",
          "required": true,
          "default": "unless-stopped",
          "options": [
            "unless-stopped",
            "always",
            "on-failure",
            "no"
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "network_macvlan_ipv4_address",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Network Macvlan Ipv4 Address",
          "required": false,
          "default": ""
        },
        {
          "name": "volume_nfs_options",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Volume Nfs Options",
          "required": false,
          "default": ""
        },
        {
          "name": "volume_mount_path",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Volume Mount Path",
          "required": false,
          "default": ""
        },
        {
          "name": "volume_nfs_server",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Volume Nfs Server",
          "required": false,
          "default": ""
        },
        {
          "name": "volume_nfs_path",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Volume Nfs Path",
          "required": false,
          "default": ""
        },
        {
          "name": "network_macvlan_subnet",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Network Macvlan Subnet",
          "required": false,
          "default": ""
        },
        {
          "name": "network_name",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Network Name",
          "required": false,
          "default": ""
        },
        {
          "name": "network_macvlan_parent_interface",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Network Macvlan Parent Interface",
          "required": false,
          "default": ""
        },
        {
          "name": "network_macvlan_gateway",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Network Macvlan Gateway",
          "required": false,
          "default": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "traefik",
      "title": "Traefik",
      "variables": [
        {
          "name": "traefik_enabled",
          "type": "bool",
          "title": "Enable Traefik integration",
          "required": false,
          "default": false,
          "description": "Enable Traefik integration"
        },
        {
          "name": "traefik_entrypoint",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "The Traefik entrypoint",
          "required": true,
          "default": "web",
          "description": "The Traefik entrypoint"
        },
        {
          "name": "traefik_host",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Traefik Host",
          "required": false,
          "default": "homepage"
        },
        {
          "name": "traefik_network",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Traefik Network",
          "required": true,
          "default": "traefik"
        },
        {
          "name": "traefik_domain",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Traefik Domain",
          "required": true,
          "default": "home.arpa"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "traefik-tls",
      "title": "Traefik TLS",
      "variables": [
        {
          "name": "traefik_tls_enabled",
          "type": "bool",
          "title": "Enable Traefik TLS",
          "required": false,
          "default": false,
          "description": "Enable Traefik TLS"
        },
        {
          "name": "traefik_tls_entrypoint",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "The Traefik TLS entrypoint",
          "required": true,
          "default": "websecure",
          "description": "The Traefik TLS entrypoint"
        },
        {
          "name": "traefik_tls_certresolver",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Traefik Tls Certresolver",
          "required": true,
          "default": "cloudflare"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "ports",
      "title": "Ports",
      "variables": [
        {
          "name": "ports_http",
          "type": "int",
          "title": "External HTTP port (web interface and API)",
          "required": false,
          "default": 9120,
          "description": "External HTTP port (web interface and API)",
          "needs": [
            "traefik_enabled=false",
            "network_mode=bridge"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "resources",
      "title": "Resource Limits",
      "variables": [
        {
          "name": "resources_enabled",
          "type": "bool",
          "title": "Resources Enabled",
          "required": false,
          "default": false
        },
        {
          "name": "resources_cpu_limit",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Resources Cpu Limit",
          "required": true,
          "default": 1.0
        },
        {
          "name": "resources_cpu_reservation",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Resources Cpu Reservation",
          "required": true,
          "default": 0.25,
          "needs": [
            "swarm_enabled=true"
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "resources_memory_limit",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Resources Memory Limit",
          "required": true,
          "default": "1G"
        },
        {
          "name": "resources_memory_reservation",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Resources Memory Reservation",
          "required": true,
          "default": "512M",
          "needs": [
            "swarm_enabled=true"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "environment",
      "title": "Environment Variables",
      "variables": [
        {
          "name": "environment_enabled",
          "type": "bool",
          "title": "Configure environment variables (required)",
          "required": false,
          "default": true,
          "description": "Configure environment variables (required)"
        },
        {
          "name": "environment_database_address",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Database connection address (MongoDB or FerretDB)",
          "required": false,
          "default": "mongodb://mongo:27017",
          "description": "Database connection address (MongoDB or FerretDB)",
          "needs": [
            "environment_enabled=true"
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "environment_database_name",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Database name",
          "required": false,
          "default": "komodo",
          "description": "Database name",
          "needs": [
            "environment_enabled=true"
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "environment_database_username",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Database username (optional)",
          "required": false,
          "default": "",
          "description": "Database username (optional)",
          "needs": [
            "environment_enabled=true"
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "environment_database_password",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Database password (optional)",
          "required": false,
          "default": "",
          "description": "Database password (optional)",
          "sensitive": true,
          "needs": [
            "environment_enabled=true"
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "environment_jwt_secret",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "JWT secret for authentication (auto-generated if empty)",
          "required": false,
          "default": "",
          "description": "JWT secret for authentication (auto-generated if empty)",
          "sensitive": true,
          "autogenerated": true,
          "needs": [
            "environment_enabled=true"
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "environment_log_level",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Log level",
          "required": false,
          "default": "info",
          "description": "Log level",
          "options": [
            "debug",
            "info",
            "warn",
            "error"
          ],
          "needs": [
            "environment_enabled=true"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "swarm",
      "title": "Docker Swarm",
      "variables": [
        {
          "name": "swarm_enabled",
          "type": "bool",
          "title": "Enable Docker Swarm mode",
          "required": false,
          "default": false,
          "description": "Enable Docker Swarm mode"
        },
        {
          "name": "swarm_placement_host",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "The placement host",
          "required": false,
          "default": "",
          "description": "The placement host"
        },
        {
          "name": "swarm_placement_mode",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "The placement mode",
          "required": false,
          "default": "replicated",
          "description": "The placement mode"
        },
        {
          "name": "swarm_replicas",
          "type": "int",
          "title": "The number of replicas",
          "required": false,
          "default": 1,
          "description": "The number of replicas"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "legacy": {
    "schema": "1.2"
  }
}
